    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>London</placeName>
                <date><add>?</add> 23. '56</date>
            </p>
            <p>My dear friend <addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Will you inform<lb/> me, at what price you can<lb/> deliver say one
                or two thousand<lb/> copies of your small Bible in<lb/> sheets, as binding is
                cheaper<lb/> here than with you. I think<lb/> your prospectus <add>?</add> $1â€”<lb/>
                I believe they could be used<lb/> here at about 5. shillings to<lb/> 5 shillings
                &amp; sixpence English<lb/> currency, &amp; the Exchange being <lb/>in your favor
                &amp; the freight<lb/> by sailing vessels not heavy<lb/> &amp; are in hopes of
                getting you<lb/> an order. Your agent here<lb/> has sold out what you sent<lb/> but
                the price is considered<lb/> exhorbitant. Let me hear<lb/> fully from you in this
                &amp;</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>any collateral <add>?</add> at, and<lb/> write me in such manner<lb/> as to enable me
                to hand<lb/> your letter to some gentlemen<lb/> here who may thereupon<lb/> send you
                an order. Of course<lb/> you will save all commissions<lb/> in filling any order
                emanating<lb/> through one and this, should<lb/> become a part of your<lb/>
                calculation. I thank you<lb/> for the Occident sent. If I<lb/> can serve you I
                shall<lb/> do it, I have only seen<lb/>
                <persName>Dr. Adler</persName> for a short time<lb/> as my time is full
                occupied<lb/> Wishing you health and<lb/> peace of mind I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">as ever yours very truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">G Kursheedt</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="The following is written upside down at the bottom of the page">I see the
                Occident comes to <persName><add>?</add> Moses</persName><lb/> so you need not send
                me more</p>
        </body>
    </text>
